  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Asia, Europe and North America. The aim of this observational
      study is to evaluate the safety of NovoPen Echo® by collecting safety information (incidence
      of technical complaints related to adverse reactions). Study duration: 12-18 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
